Dr Sindi Van Zyl was laid to rest on Thursday in a private ceremony. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Dr Sindi Van Zyl has been remembered as a loving, generous and kind person. She was laid to rest on Thursday in a private ceremony. READ: Tributes stream in for Dr Sindi van Zyl Her friends and family praised her generosity and her ability to use social media platforms to educate the public on health issues. Van Zyl’s children and husband gave a moving tribute, saying she was a great friend, sister and wife. She died on Saturday due to COVID-19 related complications after spending several weeks in an intensive care unit.